, NY, including 8 indoor options.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Data refreshed weekly</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Live availability coming soon</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Long Beach dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/parks/newyork/dogs-for-sale/dogs-for-sale-1.jpg\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Long Beach</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Long Beach<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Verified ratings, review volume, and park availability updated directly from our community directory.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Community rating</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">4.7</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Average rating across every verified listing in Long Beach. Reflects cleanliness, amenities, and community feedback.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Verified reviews</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value