ices and Store today to schedule your dog's visit\",\"slug\":\"fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store\",\"address\":\"832 Grand Blvd\",\"street\":\"832 Grand Blvd\",\"city\":\"Long Beach\",\"state\":\"NY\",\"zipCode\":\"11729\",\"full_address\":\"832 Grand Blvd, Deer Park, NY 11729, USA\",\"latitude\":40.761559,\"longitude\":-73.3077201,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJe7JfHscl6IkR6nKESm2swKg\",\"phone\":\"(631) 208-5302\",\"website\":\"http://fluiddynamicsinternational.com/\",\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":107,\"userRatingsTotal\":107,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Closed\",\"Tuesday\":\"Closed\",\"Wednesday\":\"Closed\",\"Thursday\":\"11:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"11:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"11:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"11:00 AM – 5:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/newyork/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store/fluid-dynamics-aquarium-services-and-store-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJOzWr6JJvwokRFusGiOCghls\",\"name\":\"Fur-U\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Fur-U provides essential services for Long Beach's dogs. This facility features spacious exercise zones, knowledgeable animal handlers, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. centrally located for Long Beach residents. Book your dog's stay at Fur-U today\",\"slug\":\"fur-u\",\"address\":\"966 W Beech St\",\"street\":\"966 W Beech St\",\"city\":\"Long Beach\",\"state\":\"N